data.text:
How tidy was your room when you left this morning?

If I’m being honest, it wasn’t very tidy. I usually make my bed, but there were clothes thrown all over the room. I’m the type of person who does everything at the last minute, so I’m rushing around with no time to tidy up.

Which albums are you listening to most right now?

I like different music including dance, R&B, house and even classical. But at home, the album I’m listening to the most at the moment is by an urban artist called Ray J.
